{"tid":1469593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳呀伯：屌你老母元秋！","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:30:07.000Z","uid":294142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2f5eecf83e5991dc1397a260d5656fecc33e7f","tid":1469593,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"其實好多銀髮族講野好中笑點<br />\n琴晚派口罩站 有位牙都甩晒嘅呀伯發言<br />\n係到些牙比大家開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀伯：<br />\n嗰個乜撚嘢...元秋...呀！蔣麗芸！<br />\n你係咪戇鳩到咁撚樣呀！<br />\n你老母叫陳同佳翻台灣自首？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母元秋！叫人自首咁撚叻，<br />\n你唔撚叫劉鑾雄翻澳門自首？</span><br />\n你都戇鳩！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;鼓掌&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（琴晚圍MTR咁和理非都有解散軍我屌你老母）"},{"pid":"bcd833f8b2db42d1732bbdeb86e80f09cdd8e143","tid":1469593,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"其實真 元秋 都幾慘"},{"pid":"a8dcdb13edf222d167a1346b4e648adc750266bf","tid":1469593,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd833f8b2db42d1732bbdeb86e80f09cdd8e143","tid":1469593,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"其實真 元秋 都幾慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"日日比人屌for no reason <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fa33bcfece23b00f8a59d7ded0e84c641e616b","tid":1469593,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac